- Entry point: [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx)
- Layout: [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx)
- Main styles: [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css)
- Supplementary styles: [src/app/brutalist.css](mdc:src/app/brutalist.css)

